title: Printing some primes (Hard)
text:
The problem statement is really simple (the constraints maybe not). You are to write all primes less than 109.InputThere is no input.OutputTo make the problem less output related write out only the 1st, 501st, 1001st, ... 1st mod 500.ExampleInput:Output:2
3581
7927
...
999978527
999988747
999999151
